      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a good-condition example that has been cared for and presents as a solid, enjoyable driver. It is not a mint or show-quality vehicle, but it shows better than many older cars and appears to have been kept up over time rather than neglected. Expect normal age-related cosmetic wear and signs of use throughout, but nothing that takes away from it being a respectable, usable vehicle. Overall, this is a well-sorted car for someone looking for a dependable driver-quality example they can enjoy without paying top-tier money for a collector-level one.",
