      "description": "Budget-friendly and honestly represented, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation for the right buyer. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values price, practicality, and opportunity over cosmetics. A sensible choice for a commuter, project, or backup vehicle, offered at a compelling price from a seller focused on clear, trustworthy listings.",
