      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a budget-friendly way to get on the road. Great for someone who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, whether you need basic transport, a first project, or a handy runabout. Priced fairly for what it is, and sold with a straightforward, honest approach.",
