      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, lived-in character that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s a budget-friendly ride with personality\u2014perfect for someone who wants dependable basic transportation, a handy runabout, or a rewarding project to make their own. There\u2019s a rugged charm here that you just don\u2019t get from cookie-cutter commuter cars, and with a little vision, it could be a great fit for daily errands, weekend tinkering, or as an affordable backup vehicle. Priced to move and full of potential.",
